text: Nabokov () is a surname. Notable people with the surname include: * Vladimir Vladimirovich Nabokov (1899–1977), Russian-American author, entomologist, and chess problem composer * Vladimir Dmitrievich Nabokov (1870–1922), Russian criminologist, journalist, and liberal politician, and father of Vladimir Vladimirovich Nabokov * Nicolas Nabokov (1903–1978), Russian-American composer, cousin of Vladimir Vladimirovich Nabokov * Dmitri Nabokov (1934–2012), singer and author, son of Vladimir Vladimirovich Nabokov * Evgeni Nabokov, a retired professional ice hockey goaltender Category:Russian- language surnames
